# This is a PUBLIC repo used only to host the genericized run-of-show on GitHub Pages.
# Keep internal, client-identified source (markdown, client-named HTML, backups) OUT of it.
# Only the genericized index.html is published.
*.md
syllabi/
*.BACKUP.html
daybook/
daybook-origin.git/
daybook-demos/

# skills-pack/ IS published in this repo (the attendee skills pack). Re-include it —
# its many .md files (SKILL.md, README.md, reference docs) would otherwise be caught by *.md above.
!skills-pack/**/*.md
!skills-pack/README.md

# guides/ is published too (facilitator guides) — re-include past the *.md rule above.
!guides/**/*.md
